Brothers Want Each Other Dead | Blood Twins | Crime Thriller

*Blood Brothers (AKA Identical)* - In a gripping tale of duality and obsession, identical twins emerge into a world that embraces one while cursing the other. Bound by a sinister connection, they embody the clash between good and evil, each loathing the very existence of the other. Their intense rivalry ignites when both fall for the same enchanting woman, spiraling into a volatile love triangle that culminates in a shocking act of murder that will forever alter their fates.

2011.  Stars: Jonathan Togo, Emily Baldoni, Aaron Refvem
